Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.52,0:18:10.90,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H171C23&\c&HD1D1D1&}我会很孤单的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.57,0:18:13.98,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD1D1D1&\3c&H171C23&}没事的
